beer.beer_description:
Beechy XPA (FKA Summer Ale) is a beer that can trace its roots back to our first commercial brew, in the original brewery in Ben’s dads shed back in 2005.  This beer has been really dialled in through tasting our range, reviewing recipes and hop profiles over the past 6 months, but relies on our 13 year brewing and industry experience.

This all translates into the beer we have created, an aromatic Australian summer ale with a punchy hop aroma, low pallet weight and a clean drying finish with moderate to low bitterness.
